# 🧩 Architecture & Environment Rules

## Project Structure
```
src/
├── app/ (App Router pages)
├── components/
│   ├── ui/ (shadcn primitives)
│   ├── features/ (widgets/forms/modals)
│   ├── providers/ (auth/i18n/theme/loading)
│   └── shared/ (skeletons, utilities)
├── hooks/
├── i18n/
├── lib/
│   ├── api/
│   ├── stores/
│   ├── validators/
│   └── utils/
└── __tests__/
```

> **FE-only rules**
> - ❌ No `"use server"`, `app/api/*`, or secrets
> - ✅ Only `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` envs  
> - ✅ Network via `src/lib/http.ts`

## Core Stack
Next.js 15+, React 19, TypeScript 5, TailwindCSS 4, shadcn/ui, Jotai, Zod, RHF, next-intl, Jest, ESLint, Prettier.

## Yarn scripts
```bash
yarn dev / build / start / lint / format / test
yarn dlx shadcn add button card input
```
Always commit `yarn.lock`.
